There’s a restraining order from the court.

00:45:52.720 --> 00:45:54.560
You're not allowed to harass me.

00:45:55.200 --> 00:45:56.200
What are you talking about?

00:45:56.680 --> 00:45:58.040
I’m here on my own business.

00:45:58.280 --> 00:45:59.280
What business?

00:46:02.160 --> 00:46:03.160
Don't be nosy.

00:46:03.680 --> 00:46:06.160
- You hag! - Don't.

00:46:07.160 --> 00:46:09.080
Pornapha is here to claim the insurance money

00:46:09.440 --> 00:46:12.080
her late husband left her before he passed, just like you.

00:46:12.840 --> 00:46:14.680
- Late husband’s insurance money? - Late husband’s insurance money?

00:46:15.640 --> 00:46:16.640
Yes.

00:46:17.240 --> 00:46:20.720
Wait, is your husband really dead?

00:46:21.080 --> 00:46:23.880
Or are you making this up to scam the company?

00:46:24.480 --> 00:46:26.600
You need to investigate further, Wisit.

00:46:26.760 --> 00:46:29.080
Don’t let her take any money. Do a thorough check.

00:46:29.240 --> 00:46:31.920
Wisit, her husband’s not dead.

00:46:32.120 --> 00:46:33.640
They’re still in court.

00:46:34.080 --> 00:46:36.920
She’s a scammer trying to get insurance money.

00:46:37.040 --> 00:46:40.319
You’re the scammer. I have all the documents.

00:46:40.320 --> 00:46:42.200
- Look at mine. - Have a look at mine.

00:46:42.280 --> 00:46:45.160
Don’t accuse me. I’m not a scammer. Look at this.

00:46:45.400 --> 00:46:47.880
Look at mine. Mine’s real. Yours is fake.

00:47:05.040 --> 00:47:06.040
You’re not a scammer.

00:47:06.920 --> 00:47:07.920
I’m not either.

00:47:10.400 --> 00:47:11.400
Then who is?

00:47:33.840 --> 00:47:36.960
Trying to win doesn’t help anyone.

00:47:37.400 --> 00:47:40.200
The more you want to win, the more you lose control.

00:47:41.520 --> 00:47:42.520
I’m Ake.

00:47:43.280 --> 00:47:44.360
I’m a surgeon here.

00:47:44.880 --> 00:47:46.880
Do you have to dress so young around that girl?

00:47:47.880 --> 00:47:50.320
Where are your glasses? Where did you get the clothes from?

00:47:51.120 --> 00:47:52.160
She asked me to wear them.

00:47:52.760 --> 00:47:53.760
What?

00:47:53.840 --> 00:47:55.720
Are you sure this land belongs to you?

00:47:55.920 --> 00:47:56.920
I am.

00:47:57.240 --> 00:47:58.520
I remember this tree.

00:47:59.120 --> 00:48:00.959
Ake, I’m not dumb.

00:48:00.960 --> 00:48:03.679
How dare you try to scam me? You’ll definitely pay for this.

00:48:03.680 --> 00:48:06.880
Calm down. Let’s plan carefully.

00:48:07.240 --> 00:48:09.280
We’ll outsmart him when he least expects it.

00:48:09.560 --> 00:48:10.960
He scammed us, so we scam him back.

00:48:14.920 --> 00:48:18.600
A new, fabulous kind of treatment.

00:48:18.920 --> 00:48:20.920
I want everyone to smell this.

00:48:21.240 --> 00:48:22.480
- All right. - Billiant.

00:48:22.600 --> 00:48:25.159
If someone says your mother is dangerous, what do you say?

00:48:25.160 --> 00:48:26.760
That's my mother, not me.

00:48:27.760 --> 00:48:29.720
- She's not defending her. - Not going to protect your mother?

00:48:32.320 --> 00:48:34.120
- Tim. - Cut.

00:48:34.280 --> 00:48:35.399
Why were you smiling?

